      "writtenOn": "2019-03-04T04:25:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t have strong opinion, but I thought I often see the word \u0027full\u0027 more in this kind of context... (I guess it comes from full coverage or something...)?\nAnyway, +1 to hear derat@\u0027s opinion.",
      "parentUuid": "1d5af69a_9f06fc93",
      "revId": "686a9e4f2db4dde5116992c3b8447461e4dcb879",
