      "writtenOn": "2019-03-04T06:59:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i agree re \"full\" feeling a bit ambiguous on its own. i\u0027m having a hard time coming up with a short name that will be descriptive enough here -- i think that in any case, people are going to need to look at the docs to figure out that \"android\" doesn\u0027t include master-arc-dev but that this one does. i think that \"android_all\" feels a bit clearer than the alternatives, though. in the test, i\u0027d probably recommend including a comment like this:\n\nSoftwareDeps: []string{\n    \"android_all\", // run on master-arc-dev as well\n},\n\npart of me wonders if it would\u0027ve been better to support boolean expressions in test dependencies, since then arc.Boot could use \"android || android_master\".",
      "parentUuid": "b391ffdb_58b4dd2f",
      "revId": "686a9e4f2db4dde5116992c3b8447461e4dcb879",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "4630914b_ad32a7ad",
        "filename": "src/chromiumos/cmd/local_test_runner/main.go",
