      "writtenOn": "2019-03-04T07:10:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If we want to clean up everything, I would introduce something like:\n\n- android_n\n- android_p\n- android_released (\u003d N + P)\n- android_all (\u003d N + P + master)\n\nand remove \"android\" (because it\u0027s not very clear what it means). But it might be too much for the current purpose.",
      "parentUuid": "1060de3f_da4696e5",
      "revId": "686a9e4f2db4dde5116992c3b8447461e4dcb879",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
